&lt;p&gt;Vixxo is seeking a full-time, field-based Market Manager to join our team out of our Dallas, TX office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
