&lt;li&gt;Outstanding customer service skills are required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum two years of previous experience as a Facilities Coordinator or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have a basic understanding of facilities repairs, including plumbing, electrical, and HVAC.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to operate general office equipment such as computer, copier, fax machine, scanner, and multi-line telephone system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must possess excellent time management skills and be adaptable to change.&lt;/li&gt;
